textAnnotations.description:
geoffrey sed himself to consider the
movement of the Pently. It had passed
him at the tem porasty bridge
over the
Tastaro at a few minuter past ten on the
previous night. He worked out the listance
on the presumphon that its route had beer
through Florence and house and ther
Holy via Foggia to Barletta..
across
It came to just over six hundred
miler.
